      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NATURALLY GIRL (2) resumed from a break finishing seventh (23.38) at Warrnambool in a Grade 5. Strike rate this distance strong having won three of four tries. Has ability and is a key runner. AFTERGLOW GIRL (1) boasts strong form at this course and distance having won two times from three starts. Missed the frame latest (23.52) when eighth over 390m at Warrnambool in a Mix 6/7. Looks one of the chances. BOURNE DRAMA (8) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 400m behind Rough Girl Ruby (24.32) in a TG1-4W. Placed at her previous run. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Should be about the money. DIMORA BERNIE (5) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
